{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.560", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit Freude habe ich vernommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.160", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die FDP mit ihrem Antrag auf Ausweitung von Kinderwunschbehandlungen sich des Themas der Fortpflanzung annimmt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist die zentrale Aufgabe der Gesellschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.600", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich der Weitergabe des Lebens anzunehmen und daf\u00fcr entsprechende Rahmenbedingungen zu schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.600", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in der Bundesrepublik Familien und werdende Familien unterst\u00fctzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Artikel\u00a06 des Grundgesetzes ist dies verfassungsrechtlich verb\u00fcrgt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP will mit ihrem Antrag nun eine Ausweitung der Kinderwunschbehandlungen erreichen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Gesellschaft sollte eine kinderfreundlichere Gesellschaft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wie kann unsere Gesellschaft eine Gesellschaft werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die der Weitergabe des Lebens mehr Achtung schenkt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.280", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dies auf eine andere Art und Weise geschehen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als von der FDP in ihrem Antrag gefordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir geht es dabei nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob etwas verboten oder erlaubt werden sollte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.600", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir geht es darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.880", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob ich etwas f\u00fcr so f\u00f6rderungsw\u00fcrdig halte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es von allen B\u00fcrgern bezahlt werden soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.080", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Art und Weise, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sich der Staat des Themas annehmen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und meine darauf beruhenden \u00dcberlegungen zu dem Thema m\u00f6chte ich im Folgenden darlegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.960", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Antrag der FDP auf Ausweitung von Kinderwunschbehandlungen fu\u00dft ja auf der \u00dcberzeugung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es ein Recht auf Elternschaft gebe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Mediziner kann ich Ihnen sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.480", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Recht auf Elternschaft gibt es leider nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Leben ist immer ein Geschenk, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch die Weitergabe des Lebens muss als Geschenk gesehen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit Kinderwunschbehandlungen kann man zwar nachhelfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es zum Geschenk einer Elternschaft kommt,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.560", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber ein Recht l\u00e4sst sich hieraus nicht ableiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Reproduktionsmedizin ist auch nicht in allen F\u00e4llen ein erfolgreiches und zuverl\u00e4ssiges Allheilmittel bei Kinderlosigkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Diskussion \u00fcber k\u00fcnstliche Befruchtung muss daher differenziert gef\u00fchrt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine k\u00fcnstliche Befruchtung stellt einen gravierenden medizinischen Eingriff dar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der erhebliche Nebenwirkungen wie \u00dcberstimulation mit sich bringen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zudem f\u00fchrt nur jede siebte Behandlung \u00fcberhaupt zu einer Geburt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Eingriff, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.560", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nicht erfolgreich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat h\u00e4ufig erhebliche psychosoziale Folgen f\u00fcr die Betroffenen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.760", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher ist es richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass einem entsprechenden Eingriff eine Beratung vorangestellt wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sinnvoll ist auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.920", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Bundesgesetzgeber sowie die Krankenkassen bestimmte Vorgaben f\u00fcr die Bezuschussung definieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So sind f\u00fcr die Bezuschussung ein gewisses Alter sowie eine m\u00f6glichst stabile Beziehung der Betroffenen und damit auch der m\u00f6glichen Kinder wichtige Voraussetzungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem entspricht auch das Bundessozialgericht mit seiner Entscheidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Krankenkassen keine Leistungen bei nichtverheirateten Paaren erbringen d\u00fcrfen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nur in dem Institut der Ehe existiert die gesetzliche Verpflichtung zur Verantwortungs\u00fcbernahme. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ist die einzige Form, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.200", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Paaren einen Anspruch auf gegenseitigen Unterhalt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.360", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Versorgungsausgleich und Erbschaft garantiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.160", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von dieser Sicherheit f\u00fcr beide Partner profitieren unmittelbar auch die Kinder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.040", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn der Staat den weitreichenden Schritt einer k\u00fcnstlichen Befruchtung aktiv finanziell unterst\u00fctzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.280", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollte er im Sinne der Kinder auch Bedingungen f\u00fcr eine gr\u00f6\u00dftm\u00f6gliche Stabilit\u00e4t formulieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.720", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Des Weiteren bin ich aber auch aus grunds\u00e4tzlichen Erw\u00e4gungen heraus gegen eine Ausweitung der Kinderwunschbehandlungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.920", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meiner \u00dcberzeugung nach ist der Mensch n\u00e4mlich ein Gesch\u00f6pf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.320", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entspringend aus der sch\u00f6pferischen Liebe zweier Geschlechter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.640", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich idealerweise dann auch dieses Gesch\u00f6pfs annehmen und Verantwortung hierf\u00fcr tragen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.960", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr mich stellt sich damit vielmehr die Frage: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.200", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was k\u00f6nnen wir als Gesellschaft im Allgemeinen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.280", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als Bundestag im Speziellen tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.960", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Eltern in ihrer wichtigen Aufgabe zu unterst\u00fctzen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was k\u00f6nnen wir tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich wieder mehr Paare f\u00fcr die Weitergabe des Lebens entscheiden?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.800", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ist es f\u00fcr mich entscheidend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Wert des Lebens als solchem wieder einen anderen Stellenwert zu geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konkret sollte daher nicht die Kinderwunschbehandlung ausgeweitet werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern Frauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bereits in Schwangerschaft sind und in Konfliktsituationen stehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.880", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten vom Staat besser betreut werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir uns die Zahlen an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Abtreibungen in Deutschland nehmen ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar nicht nur in absoluten Zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.800", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch im Verh\u00e4ltnis pro Geburt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.240", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gro\u00dfe Aber: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.800", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Immer noch werden pro 100\u00a0Geburten in Deutschland 13 werdende Menschen abgetrieben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fast 100\u00a0000\u00a0Abtreibungen werden derzeit in Deutschland pro Jahr vorgenommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar weit \u00fcber 90\u00a0Prozent nach Beratungsgespr\u00e4ch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.600", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.120", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in mehr als neun von zehn F\u00e4llen liegen bei der Schwangerschaft weder Krankheit noch Gef\u00e4hrdung der Mutter vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben also \u00fcber 90\u00a0000\u00a0Abtreibungen pro Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.080", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig werden aber knapp 4\u00a0000\u00a0Kinder pro Jahr in Deutschland adoptiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.040", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und davon nur 1\u00a0500\u00a0Kinder von nichtverwandten Personen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.320", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig ist in Deutschland fast jedes zehnte Paar ungewollt kinderlos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.320", 
